{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"http://ghost.local:8000","title":"Docs","description":"Everything you need to know about working with the Ghost professional publishing platform."}},"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"MouseEvent","date":"2019-04-25","date_pretty":"25 April, 2019","path":null,"meta_title":null,"meta_description":null,"image":null,"next":null,"sidebar":"javascript","toc":null,"keywords":["MouseEvent","javascript"]},"html":"<h2 id=\"clientx-和-clienty\"><a href=\"#clientx-%E5%92%8C-clienty\" aria-label=\"clientx 和 clienty permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>clientX 和 clientY</h2>\n<p>事件发生时的应用客户端区域的水平坐标 (与页面坐标不同)。例如，不论页面是否有水平滚动，当你点击客户端区域的左上角时，鼠标事件的 clientX 值都将为 0 。最初这个属性被定义为长整型（long integer），如今 CSSOM 视图模块将其重新定义为双精度浮点数（double float）</p>\n<h2 id=\"screenx-和-screeny\"><a href=\"#screenx-%E5%92%8C-screeny\" aria-label=\"screenx 和 screeny permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>screenX 和 screenY</h2>\n<p>相对于设备屏幕左上角（0，0）的坐标</p>\n<h2 id=\"offsetx-和-offsety\"><a href=\"#offsetx-%E5%92%8C-offsety\" aria-label=\"offsetx 和 offsety permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>offsetX 和 offsetY</h2>\n<p>事件对象与目标节点的内填充边（padding edge）在 X 轴和 Y 轴方向上的偏移量。</p>\n<h1 id=\"pagex-和-pagey\"><a href=\"#pagex-%E5%92%8C-pagey\" aria-label=\"pagex 和 pagey permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>pageX 和 pageY</h1>\n<p>相对于整个网页左上角（0，0）的坐标</p>","fields":{"slug":"/reference/javascript/mouseevent/"},"timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"clientX 和 clientY 事件发生时的应用客户端区域的水平坐标 (与页面坐标不同)。例如，不论页面是否有水平滚动，当你点击客户端区域的左上角时，鼠标事件的 clientX 值都将为 0 。最初这个属性被定义为长整型（long integer），如今 CSSOM…","fileAbsolutePath":"/home/travis/build/jolylai/docs/content/reference/javascript/mouseevent.md"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/reference/javascript/mouseevent/"}}